short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Makes ReasonML types more readable when they are logged to the console.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Transforms ReasonML types objects to a more readable format when they are logged to the Chrome console or NodeJS console.

The Chrome extension will only work if you enable Custom Formatters in the DevTools settings.
